OL,3,CHurricane Melissa: How to support the
OL,4,Caid effort in Jamaica
OL,6,FThe UK government has published key
OL,7,Fadvice for those wanting to help
OL,8,Fpeople in Jamaica recover from the
OL,9,Fimpact of Hurricane Melissa.
OL,11,FThe category five hurricane made
OL,12,Flandfall on Tuesday 28 October, with
OL,13,Ftop winds of 185mph making it one of
OL,14,Fthe strongest Atlantic hurricanes on
OL,15,Frecord.
