OL,3,CHurricane Melissa: How to support the
OL,4,Caid effort in Jamaica
OL,6,FDespite advance warnings and
OL,7,Fpreparation for the impact of Melissa,
OL,8,Fthe emergency response has been slow,
OL,9,Fwhich Jamaican officials blame on the
OL,10,Fhurricane's power and on destroyed
OL,11,Froad infrastructure.
OL,13,FThe foreign office has now provided
OL,14,Frecommendations on how best to support
OL,15,FJamaicans and others in the Caribbean
OL,16,Fin the aftermath of the storm.
OL,18,FOn its website, the foreign office
OL,19,Fsays "one of the most effective ways"
OL,20,Fto help is to donate money to trusted
OL,21,Fcharities and aid organisations.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/5
