OL,3,CHurricane Melissa: How to support the
OL,4,Caid effort in Jamaica
OL,6,FIt stresses that donations made this
OL,7,Fway can be transferred quickly to
OL,8,Fwhere help is most urgently required,
OL,9,Fwarning that physical goods could
OL,10,Fhinder relief efforts.
OL,12,F"Unsolicited donations of goods,
OL,13,Falthough well-intentioned, can
OL,14,Fobstruct supply chains and delay life-
OL,15,Fsaving assistance," the website says.
OL,17,F"If you wish to donate goods, check
OL,18,Fwith charities and community groups
OL,19,Ffirst. They will have lists of items
OL,20,Fthey need."
