OL,3,CHurricane Melissa: How to support the
OL,4,Caid effort in Jamaica
OL,6,FPeople are advised to select charities
OL,7,Fwho are experienced in disaster relief
OL,8,Fand to check the charity's name and
OL,9,Fthe country it is registered in, to
OL,10,Fensure it is genuine.
OL,12,FThe government has recommended trusted
OL,13,Forganisations, such as Jamaica's
OL,14,Femergency appeal or the International
OL,15,FFederation of Red Cross and Red
OL,16,FCrescent (IFRC) Societies appeal, to
OL,17,Fsend funds.
OL,19,FThey add that they will match public
OL,20,Fdonations to the IFRC appeal up to #1
OL,21,Fmillion.
